over:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-baby-name-according-to-numerology\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">Numerology Baby Names: Full Number-by-Number List for 2026</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Learn how numerology is used in baby naming, how name numbers are calculated, and what parents should consider when selecting a name using numerological principles.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-baby-name-according-to-date-of-birth\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">Choosing a Baby Name by Date of Birth</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Discover how many cultures use a child&#x27;s date of birth when selecting a meaningful name and learn the factors parents commonly consider during the naming process.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-baby-name-in-islam\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-700\">Islamic Naming Guides</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">How to Choose a Baby Name in Islam</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Learn the Islamic guidelines for choosing a baby name, the importance of meaningful names, and the factors Muslim parents should consider before making a final decision.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/how-to-choose-a-baby-name-that-ages-well\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-700\">Baby Naming Guides</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">How to Choose a Baby Name That Ages Well</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Discover how to choose a baby name that remains relevant from childhood to adulthood. Learn what makes a name timeless, professional, memorable, and adaptable across generations.</p></a><a class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-blue-300\" href=\"/stories/baby-names-inspired-by-nature\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-blue-700\">Baby Name Lists</span><h3 class=\"mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-slate-950\">Baby Names Inspired by Nature</h3><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600\">Nature-inspired baby names have never felt more relevant. Whether you&#x27;re drawn to the wild, the sky, the sea, or the garden, this guide covers the most beautiful nature names across every category — with the depth and detail to help you choose wisely.</p></a></div></section></main></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-slate-200 bg-white\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.3fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 text-white\"><img alt=\"NameVerse logo\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"30\" height=\"30\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"object-contain\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/logo.png\"/></div><div><div class=\"text-lg font-black tracking-tight text-slate-950\">NameVerse</div><div class=\"text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500\">Meanings, origins &amp; guides</div></div></a><p class=\"mt-5 max-w-sm text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-600\">NameVerse helps parents and researchers discover baby names with meanings, cultural origins, linguistic context and trusted naming guidance.</p><div class=\"mt-6 flex gap-2\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/NameVerseOfficial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" class=\"grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded